Key Match Events: Ja Morant scored 26 points with 10 rebounds and 14 assists to lead the Memphis Grizzlies to a 122-99 victory over the Milwaukee Bucks
Post-Match Reflections: Ja Morant: "I just came out being aggressive, took what the defence gave me"
Miscellaneous Highlights: Giannis Antetokounmpo scored 37 points and grabbed 11 rebounds for the Bucks but teammate Damian Lillard was held to four points on 1-of-12 shooting
Others: Brook Lopez was Milwaukee's next-highest scorer with 12 points
The Bucks dropped their fourth straight after opening the season with a win over injury-hit Philadelphia
